org.grouplens.grapht.reflect

Class AbstractSatisfactionVisitor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.grapht.reflect.AbstractSatisfactionVisitor<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SatisfactionVisitor<T>

    public abstract class AbstractSatisfactionVisitor<T>
extends Object
implements SatisfactionVisitor<T>
    Abstract implementation of SatisfactionVisitor. All methods delegate to visitDefault(), which in turn returns a default value.
    Since:
    0.5
    Author:
    GroupLens Research
